name: Rocket Quest Lite
description:
Emu is back! But this time he got a jet pack and finds himself in outer space. This quirky version of an old arcade game will keep you entertained for hours with different speed settings and six different game tracks on the full version. Start off easy and work your way up and discover the surprises Emu has in store.

So, Emu is packed and ready to skyrocket through the galaxies. He just needs your quick fingers to guide him on his adventure.


Download now and start playing.

Check out all the other apps from Tim O's Studios
